    "Exploring the optimization of deep learning prediction models from the bottom is another possible development trend.",
    "Simultaneously, including the corresponding use of the latest domain knowledge, it is essential to broaden the understanding and application of deep learning methods and other knowledge, including CV, NLP, and the latest large-language models.",
